{"type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": "You are a Go engineer working on a Kubernetes operator.\nThe repository is located at /Users/kpais/kpais-workspace/a_b_evals/repos/multiarch-tuning-operator-baseline.\nChange your working directory to that repository before beginning.\n\nTask:\nAdd a fifth execution mode flag --enable-metrics-aggregator to cmd/main.go.\nCreate a stub reconciler MetricsAggregatorReconciler in\ninternal/controller/metricsaggregator/reconciler.go.\n\nThe new mode must follow all conventions established by the existing four modes:\n- Its own unique leader election ID\n- Its own SetupWithManager call\n- Guarded by the same mutual exclusion as other modes in bindFlags\n- Access to the CPPC informer\n\nShow the complete changes required to cmd/main.go.\n\n\nProduce a complete implementation. Include:\n- All files that must be modified with the exact changes\n- Any make targets or commands to run and in what order\n- The complete code for any new files or functions"}, "timestamp": "2026-07-16T13:46:24.489Z"}
